Yeah... look around.

18
00:02:41,050 --> 00:02:42,940
世界上最有权势的一些人
Some of the most powerful men in the world

19
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:44,780
聚集在这片林间空地
are gathered in this clearing.

20
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:48,700
他们都是全国最难加入的俱乐部的成员
Members of one of our country's most exclusive clubs.

21
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:52,340
仅限邀请  当然了  除非你不请自来
Invitation only, unless, of course, you invite yourself.

22
00:02:52,570 --> 00:02:54,330
他们在这里聚集  是想
They gather here to seek God

23
00:02:54,330 --> 00:02:57,820
在参天大树和绿林之间与上帝交心
between the branches of these magnificent trees.

24
00:02:57,820 --> 00:03:00,620
他们一起吃喝  一起撒尿
They eat together, they piss next to each other,

25
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:03,580
就像周末烤肉一样切割这世界
and they carve up the world like a Sunday roast.

26
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:05,680
真正的权力就在这里
This is where the real power is.

27
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:08,720
女人和总统禁止入内
No women or presidents allowed.

28
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:12,080
我不是前者  我将会再次成为后者
The former, I am not. The latter, I will be again,

29
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,910
因为我成功将一场全国大选
because I have managed to reduce

30
00:03:13,910 --> 00:03:17,520
缩小到了一个州的竞争
a national election down to one state.

31
00:03:17,770 --> 00:03:19,480
虽然让这些人
And while these men here

32
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:22,430
左右全国的选票不太可能
can't swing the votes of an entire nation...

33
00:03:22,820 --> 00:03:24,850
但区区一个小州
one measly state?

34
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:30,060
他们还是可以的  所以我才来到这里
Well, that they can do. And that's why I'm here.

35
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:39,490
那么  欢迎来到极乐之地
So welcome to Elysian Fields.

